  "body": "<p>Last month we wrapped up a big packet project. </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/0538bd161820e940.jpg?v=1782796713\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>And now we can share what was in those little glassine envelopes galore. I snapped some photos of the process for the delightful little fabric flowers we made, also known as \"yo-yo's\". </p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"20b-dsc_1898.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/8ad1447b09773f5e.jpg?v=1782796716\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"20c-dsc_1899.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/6bb4cc2bc1c87c4d.jpg?v=1782796718\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20d-dsc_1912.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/1b573a039a47f1b0.jpg?v=1782796721\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20e-dsc_0661.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/d4ba22d56d6a588d.jpg?v=1782796724\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20f-dsc_0649.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/8e16192b09cc5166.jpg?v=1782796727\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20g-dsc_0650.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/17b1fee54d5c0a17.jpg?v=1782796729\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>As you can see, we had to make a lot of these hand-sewn flowers. They can be found in Studio Calico's March kit, Story Hour. At the pre-sale for subscribers (I have been subbing for over a year), a portion of these kits were already sold out. In case you're thinking of getting one, here's the story: buy it now, before it's too late. And plant these little flowers on your paper projects.  </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"20h-scmarchkit2.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/8c9f73339788e2e6.jpg?v=1782796732\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20i-scmarch2012main283of329.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/fcf7af534fbf65b3.jpg?v=1782796735\"/>"
}